# Blossom 🌸 does NOT require a .env file.
#
# API keys are entered by each user in the in-app Token Vault and stored
# ONLY in that user's browser (localStorage). Nothing is uploaded to any cloud.
#
# This file is kept purely as a reference list of the free providers Blossom
# supports and where to get a free key. Do not put real keys here.
#
#   GROQ_API_KEY        -> https://console.groq.com/keys
#   GOOGLE_AI_API_KEY   -> https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
#   OPENROUTER_API_KEY  -> https://openrouter.ai/keys
